abstract: At least four of the “100 Best C.E.O.’s” listed in a new magazine will not be around for future lists.
snippet: At least four of the “100 Best C.E.O.’s” listed in a new magazine will not be around for future lists.
lead_paragraph: When Doubledown Media published the first issue of Corporate Leader magazine this month, it included a list of the “100 Best C.E.O.’s.” But if there is a second annual listing, at least four of those chief executives will be missing.

headline.main: The List Is Stellar, but a Little Dated
headline.print_headline: The List Is Stellar, But a Little Dated
